99999997726, \"rank\": 2.0149272704576959e-13, \"text\": \"Nine Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9069787530749627, \"rank\": 0.08489829710924, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richard Fox was quite the canoeist himself, representing Great Britain in the 1992 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9093242738632561, \"rank\": 0.09223672898473707, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.7350316242037588, \"rank\": 0.3603942647696549, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But on Wednesday, he wore the hat of a proud father first and a broadcaster second as he called his daughter's gold medal victory.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once Fox realized that his daughter's time of 96:08 would hold up as the best score of all the competitors in the event, he quickly realized that he needed to leave his commentary responsibilities to celebrate the victory.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9093242738632561, \"rank\": 0.09223672898473707, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us have a hug,\\\" said Richard Fox to his broadcast partner.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9093242738632561, \"rank\": 0.09223672898473707, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh my god, I am going; I am going.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am done.\\\"\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's obviously hard to fault Fox for his abrupt exit from the broadcast booth.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9093242738632561, \"rank\": 0.09223672898473707, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball_on_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00a0never quite reached the heights that his daughter did in the sport, finishing in fourth in the lone Olympics appearance he made in the Men's K-1 Slalom.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \